Brussel in Antonj Rosseau
J'ay bien reccu la vd. du 13 cot. avecq le toit sere comme aussi. celle du 16
avecq les 2 petites pacquets que sont enchemince ausoindhuy ensuite de vre erd
pour nieuporte & mons. Michel de valleg. j'ay donne ce soir erd mostasie
sur Brussel um petit pacquuet avecq adresse d vous contenent 10 p de dantelles
de me vol les quelles je ne cognirs pourt inscent que sont les vres, ce que
vous sara plus capable a anger, & sien cas qu'il soient quelques une deles
mienes pernn il vous plaira de me les renvoier, les aultre 3, & 3 cospors
sont & moy, del un & de l'autre vous pouves senir notice, comme se faire de mopare
a 18d.
London mr. Denry Collier
mij last to you was on the 18th curtt. sence recd. yd of 3d., my freind mr. sabatoa
att Brussels weites mee word that they say, that John vale is out of towne
so as he hath been norw forme dayes, which is a vee ill signe in so much
not one word of good from thence, & non apearence of any payment yett, thugh
hs people told m. Sabbarton, thadt as yeasterday evening he should have been
att kome, so more of that gnext. I have examined yd letters, butt I finde non
where by you mentont of £100- to mr. Browne, & £100 to m. PRckering lobeuse
neither do you note theire deus now, so in case they ball in aprivate hande, shall
not beable to finde them, yett in such an occasion you must make shift to remitt
for I am no banqer, butt with much a do hardely able enough to pay my ounes
dibts, I know not what elce you may have a unning on V. butt I must
advise you to provide for itt, because I know for certaine that I v. shall not, as to
the concernes of I fb. I doubt them despecate, whiy can you not make a step over this
snommer & take our connerey avre, & wishall cleare the rest of yd concernes, for my
part if you come, about ours, wee will make an end in 2 jours time, whilst
po intiom I'll make sluft to putt of yd. goods e so my rembourse have
been obliged to give my bill on you for £150- s to m. actus anneslay poyd
VWss att 23.5 for which please to give due konos, I shought you shoild hare
remitted mee according to yd proise I have been obliged for some consid ecators
to take in my bill on you of 28 feb. which remitt this day toHM thingh itt
pincked meer vere much beeng extreamely necessitated for many

Londen m. Benry Maynard
sence my last to you of the 11th cur recd. yd 3 d. with the incloted invoyces
for goods shipt for my half share in which shall give you creditt, I have not one
word of news yett of klarck or Londar, though I do vere much want the goods, God
send them well. pray dispatch the rest of what in ordered, finding as yett ord. for no
mone, except a pack of pure good reds, of severall prijses, as formarly adviseed
I am glad wee are to have the 6 11 selver marckes, if time permits, you
shall have hen included the note of what I sold them att, & what they rendaed
that so you may beat downe that knarsh hunnour, could wee once gett in well
with the northren goods, I w hould beat hun out here for he can not serve a man
for 2fb so all he hath is the goodnis of his goods, which keeps him hip, a his
Enstomens inchned to pass his hinnour I did not question, butt that you was muc
concerned with I V yett I hope that att a longer run, he will be able to satirfye
every body, for I look upon him to be honese, butt he hath much undon in att
Brussels in onr trade, I could wish he was able to sakifye every bady, & to leave
the wollen trade & meddle with his wifes mothers came lot fabrique, & then fure
I shall advance 4 a 5 more upowhat I shell sell att Brussels & will be no
preiudice to you for I shall putt of the more goods, I have bought 2 bales of
mothers for H.C. for which le desred mee to draw the valewon him as Idid
& because I doubt his credit doth not increase by his bills protested ad. on SV.
to tooke itt in againe a remitt itt you is due the 28h curtt for my acctt, & is
the onely & last that I gave out here, I am al most cleare from hime, & then
faw will my good freind, for I do not like his straights, whilst Intrim I shall
endeavour to remitt you as much as por., butt i you should be straihtned vere
much you know what oblig. I lave to demostrate my self
a 18d
